3 September 2009Ministers Collins Chabane and Trevor Manuel to brief the media on release of the green papers on performance monitoring and planning.The two papers describe the process and provide guidance on performance monitoring and planning for government. The green papers will be released for public comment and discussion.The briefing will be held as follows;Date: 4 September 2009 (Friday)Time: 12:00Venue: Room 159, Union Buildings, PretoriaNB: There will be a video link up to the Imbizo Media Centre, Cape Town.Enquiries: Harold Maloka Cell: 082 847 9799Issued by: Government Communications (GCIS)